milestones.description: This is the highest match aggregate (478) involving teams Australia & India in ODIs
Kapil Dev has broken the record for most catches (12) in ODIs for IND, going past Vengsarkar's 11
Australia's 163-run win against India is the largest margin of victory in terms of runs in ODIs, beating 149-run win against New Zealand
Kapil Dev has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (35) for IND, going past Vengsarkar
